akes 3 to 5 days. Express shipping takes 1 day. Express shipping is only available on non-subscription purchases.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Where do you ship? </span>We ship nationwide across Indonesia.<br><br><span style="font-weight: 700;">Can I track my order? </span>Yes. You should receive a notification in your email inbox whenever your order is dispatched.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">My ordered arrived damaged/is wrong. What should I do?&nbsp;</span>We are sorry this happened.. Email us pictures of your parcel along with your Order ID to <span style="color: rgb(88, 123, 146);">hello@umawomen.com</span>. We'll ship you a new one.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Do you accept return?</span>&nbsp;Given the intimate nature of our products, we cannot accept returns.<br><br></span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-d53f0e51 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-beed9bac accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="e3beed9b-acd5-4f0e-91e0-7e247ce953aa" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>Payment</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-9bacd53f accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="e3beed9b-acd5-4f0e-91e0-7e247ce953aa" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-c6f75510"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-8960c6f7"><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">What forms of payment do you accept?&nbsp;</span>We accepts credit card (VISA and Master Card), JENIUS, GOPAY, OVO and bank transfers. Auto-payment is only available through credit card.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Can I purchase with bank transfers? </span>Yes. Head to our <span style="color: rgb(88, 123, 146);">Shopee</span>,&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(88, 123, 146);">Tokopedia</sp